Pastikan RabbitMQ sudah hidup
Jika Anda pakai Docker, jalankan:

docker run -d --name rabbitmq-local -p 5672:5672 -p 15672:15672 rabbitmq:3-management
Setelah itu buka:

http://localhost:15672
username: guest
password: guest
Jalankan service order
Buka terminal di folder order-service lalu jalankan:
cd d:\dataku\Semester_8\Tts web\web-service-topik2-kelompok4\order-service
mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
Jalankan service inventory
Buka terminal lain di folder inventory-service lalu jalankan:
cd d:\dataku\Semester_8\Tts web\web-service-topik2-kelompok4\inventory-service
mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
